data.description: An Investors DREAM! Actual rental income last year was $56,000! So welcome to your dream beachside retreat! Nestled just steps away from the Gulf, this charming 2-bedroom, 1.5-bath townhome offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience without the burden of HOA fees. As you step inside, you'll be captivated by the tasteful upgrades that adorn the space. The downstairs area boasts a thoughtfully remodeled kitchen, complete with granite countertops, a stylish tiled backsplash, and undermount sink. The addition of brand new LVP flooring in the living room adds a touch of sophistication and complements the coastal ambiance.
